activating the Epic &amp; FBSS)<br><br><br>now work your own abacus and figure out what Gharn's rock at 16/19 be ....<br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Jun  6 16:12:25 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
